verbose_text: On the immunohistochemical staining, there was a lower expression of transforming TGF-beta1 in the Botox group (45.2 +/-4.2, the number cells with a positive TGF-beta1 expression / high power field) than that of the control group (70.2 +/-8.3, the number of cells with a positive TGF-beta1 expression / high power field) at the 4th week after surgery (XREF_TABLE, XREF_FIG).
